COMMITTEE AMENDMENT
HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES
State of Oklahoma
SPEAKER:
CHAIR:
I move to amend HB4453
Of the printed Bill
Page 3 Section 2 Lines 16
Of the Engrossed Bill
By deleting the words "Speaker of the Oklahoma House of Representatives"
and inserting in lieu thereof the following:
"Oklahoma Hospital Association"
On Page 3, Section 2, Line 18 by deleting the words "President Pro Tempore
of the Oklahoma State Senate" and inserting in lieu thereof the following:
"Healthcare Workforce Training Commission"
On Page 5, Section 3, Lines 4-7 by deleting subsection A and inserting in
lieu thereof the following:
"A. The State Coordinator for the Health Information Exchange, created in
section 1-132.1 of title 63 of the Oklahoma State Statutes, shall
establish and maintain an All Payer Claims Database (APCD) to collect and
analyze health care costs, utilization, and spending data from all payer
types operating within this state."
On Page 6, Section 4, Lines 15-16 by striking paragraph 3 of subsection B.
On Page 8, Section 7, Line 24 by inserting after the word "public." The
following language:
"The initial report shall be published no later than December 31, 2027."
AMEND TITLE TO CONFORM TO AMENDMENTS
Amendment submitted by: Carl Newton
